licativo personalizado, publicado sob o nome da sua prática ou startup.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="py-16 bg-white"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center transition-all duration-700 opacity-0 translate-y-10"><div class="lg:w-full space-y-8"><div class="inline-block"><span class="bg-green-success/20 text-green-success px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium border border-green-success/30">Cuidado Multimodal</span></div><div><h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-slate-dark mb-6 leading-tight">Cuidado Multimodal</h2><p class="text-xl text-slate-600 leading-relaxed max-w-xl">Ofereça cuidados através de todos os canais que seus pacientes preferem — todos acessíveis dentro do aplicativo.</p></div><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8"><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-calendar h-6 w-6 text-green-success flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M8 2v4"></path><path d="M16 2v4"></path><rect width="18" height="18" x="3" y="4" rx="2"></rect><path d="M3 10h18"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Consultas Presenciais</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Pacientes agendam e fazem check-in com facilidade.</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-message-square h-6 w-6 text-green-success flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 17a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H6.828a2 2 0 0 0-1.414.586l-2.202 2.202A.71.71 0 0 1 2 21.286V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h16a2 2