consultas com integrações de dispositivos.</p></div><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8"><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-smartphone h-6 w-6 text-teal-primary flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="14" height="20" x="5" y="2" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><path d="M12 18h.01"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Apple Health (iOS)</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">suporte.</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-activity h-6 w-6 text-teal-primary flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 12h-2.48a2 2 0 0 0-1.93 1.46l-2.35 8.36a.25.25 0 0 1-.48 0L9.24 2.18a.25.25 0 0 0-.48 0l-2.35 8.36A2 2 0 0 1 4.49 12H2"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Google Health Connect (Android)</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">suporte.</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-zap h-6 w-6 text-teal-primary flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M4 14a1 1 0 0 1-.78-1.63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Compatibilidade com Dispositivos Bluetooth</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Sincronize sinais vitais diretamente no registro de saúde.</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-heart h-6 w-6 text-teal-primary flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M2 9.5a5.5 5.5 0 0 1 9.591-3.676.56.56 0 0 0 .818 0A5.49 5.49 0 0 1 22 9.5c0 2.29-1.5 4-3 5.5l-5.492 5.313a2 2 0 0 1-3 .019L5 15c-1.5-1.5-3-3.2-3-5.5"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Uploads Automatizados</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Dados de saúde fluem para registros de pacientes sem esforço.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="py-16 bg-white"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="text-center mb-12"><h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 text-slate-dark">Opções para Cada Cliente</h2><div class="w-16 h-1 bg-blue-vibrant mx-auto mb-8"></div></div><div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto"><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8"><div class="bg-blue-light/10 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-blue-light"><div class="text-center mb-6"><div class="inline-block"><span class="bg-blue-vibrant/20 text-blue-vibrant px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium border border-blue-vibrant/30">Opção Gratuita</span></div></div><h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-dark mb-4 text-center">Aplicativo Gratuito ContinuousCare</h3><p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-center mb-6">Rápido para implantar, disponível imediatamente para todos os seus pacientes.</p><div class="space-y-3"><div class="flex items-center gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-check w-4 h-4 text-blue-vibrant flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg><span class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Disponibilidade imediata</span></div><div class="flex items-center gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-check w-4 h-4 text-blue-vibrant flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg><span class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Nenhuma configuração necessária</span></div><div class="flex items-center gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-check w-4 h-4 text-blue-vibrant flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg><span class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Recursos móveis principais incluídos</span></div></div></div><div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-primary/8 to-teal-primary/12 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-teal-primary/20 shadow-sm"><div class="text-center mb-6"><div class="inline-block"><span class="bg-teal-primary/20 text-teal-primary px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium border border-teal-primary/30">Complemento Opcional</span></div></div><h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-dark mb-4 text-center">Aplicativo Personalizado</h3><p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-center mb-6">Publique sob sua própria marca com integrações de dispositivos estendidas e controle total da marca.</p><div class="space-y-3"><div class="flex items-center gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-check w-4 h-4 text-teal-primary flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg><span class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Sua marca da prática</span></div><div class="flex items-center gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-check w-4 h-4 text-teal-primary flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg><span class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Mais integrações de dispositivos</span></div><div class="flex items-center gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-check w-4 h-4 text-teal-primary flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg><span class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Publicado em suas próprias contas de app store</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="py-16 bg-gray-50"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="text-center mb-12"><h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 text-slate-dark">Como Funciona</h2><div class="w-16 h-1 bg-blue-vibrant mx-auto mb-8"></div><p class="text-xl text-slate-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">Forneça aos pacientes um caminho claro e simples para usar o aplicativo móvel para Pacientes</p></div><div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto"><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8 relative"><div class="text-center relative"><div class="relative mb-6"><div class="w-20 h-20 bg-blue-vibrant/10 rounded-3xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-smartphone h-10 w-10 text-blue-vibrant" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="14" height="20" x="5" y="2" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><path d="M12 18h.01"></path></svg></div><div class="absolute -top-2 -right-2 w-8 h-8 bg-blue-vibrant text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">1</div></div><h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-dark mb-3">Baixe o Aplicativo</h3><p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Os pacientes baixam o aplicativo ContinuousCare da iOS App Store ou Google Play. Se você usa uma versão personalizada, eles baixam seu aplicativo de marca em vez disso.</p><div class="hidden lg:block absolute top-10 -right-4 text-blue-vibrant/30"><svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10.293 5.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l4 4a1 1 0 010 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L12.586 11H5a1 1 0 110-2h7.586l-2.293-2.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg></div></div><div class="text-center relative"><div class="relative mb-6"><div class="w-20 h-20 bg-teal-primary/10 rounded-3xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-shield h-10 w-10 text-teal-primary" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z"></path></svg></div><div class="absolute -top-2 -right-2 w-8 h-8 bg-teal-primary text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">2</div></div><h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-dark mb-3">Faça Login com Segurança</h3><p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Os pacientes fazem login com as mesmas credenciais que usam para o portal web Virtual Practice. Isso garante acesso seguro e uma experiência unificada entre web e mobile.</p><div class="hidden lg:block absolute top-10 -right-4 text-teal-primary/30"><svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10.293 5.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l4 4a1 1 0 010 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L12.586 11H5a1 1 0 110-2h7.586l-2.293-2.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg></div></div><div class="text-center relative"><div class="relative mb-6"><div class="w-20 h-20 bg-green-success/10 rounded-3xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-heart h-10 w-10 text-green-success" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M2 9.5a5.5 5.5 0 0 1 9.591-3.676.56.56 0 0 0 .818 0A5.49 5.49 0 0 1 22 9.5c0 2.29-1.5 4-3 5.5l-5.492 5.313a2 2 0 0 1-3 .019L5 15c-1.5-1.5-3-3.2-3-5.5"></path></svg></div><div class="absolute -top-2 -right-2 w-8 h-8 bg-green-success text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">3</div></div><h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-dark mb-3">Acesse Cuidados a Qualquer Momento</h3><p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Uma vez logados, os pacientes podem agendar consultas, visualizar registros, pagar contas e sincronizar dados de saúde do Apple Health, Google Health Connect ou dispositivos compatíveis.</p><div class="hidden lg:block absolute top-10 -right-4 text-green-success/30"><svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10.293 5.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l4 4a1 1 0 010 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L12.586 11H5a1 1 0 110-2h7.586l-2.293-2.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg></div></div><div class="text-center relative"><div class="relative mb-6"><div class="w-20 h-20 bg-purple-accent/10 rounded-3xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-bell h-10 w-10 text-purple-accent" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M10.268 21a2 2 0 0